==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[ki-]]'' (interrogative and relative [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-e]]'' (correlative suffix of place)

===Correlative===
'''kie''' (''accusative'' '''[[kien]]''')
# [[where]] (the interrogative and relative correlative of place)
#: Like other interrogative and relative correlatives, '''kie''' can be combined with ''[[ajn]]'', the adverbial particle of generality. '''''Kie''' ajn'' thus means ''[[wherever]]''.

